==Devanagari script==
=== Hindi ===
'''स'''

==== Pronunciation ====
/ s /, pronounced alone it is / sə /, similar to the English sun.

====Consonant====

The third [[sibilant]] of the [[Devanagari]] script. Linguistically it is considered an alveolar sibilant.

=== Transliteration ===
*[[w:IAST|IAST]]: s  S
*[[w:ITRANS|ITRANS]]: s

